# Baseqat Platform - Agent Instructions

## Project Structure
- **Backend**: .NET 10 Web API (`d:\ND\app\Baseqt\`)
  - `Baseqt.API/` — Controllers, Program.cs, wwwroot/uploads
  - `Baseqat.CORE/` — DTOs, Helpers (EmailTemplates, DateHelper), Services (IEmailService), Response types
  - `Baseqat.EF/` — Models, Enums, Repositories (BaseRepository), DATA (UnitOfWork, IDataUnit), Migrations
- **Frontend**: Next.js App Router + TypeScript (`d:\2026\baseqat\app\Basqat-main\`)
  - `app/(dashboard)/` — Admin dashboard pages
  - `app/(site)/` — Public site pages
  - `app/(auth)/` — Login/Register
  - `app/client-dashboard/` — Client dashboard
  - `app/api/[...path]/route.ts` — API proxy to backend
  - `services/` — Service layers (axios calls)
  - `components/` — Shared components (dashboard/, site/, client-dashboard/)
  - `lib/axios.ts` — Axios instance with interceptor (auth_token cookie)

## Architecture & Patterns
- **Backend**: Repository + Unit of Work pattern via `IDataUnit`
- **Response wrappers**: `ApiBaseResponse<T>` and `PagedResponse<T>`
  - `ApiBaseResponse` constructors are **protected** — use `Success()` / `Fail()` static methods
  - `Fail()` signature: `Fail(string message, string[] errors = null)` — cannot pass data
- **Auth**: JWT with `auth_token` cookie, `[Authorize]` attribute, custom `[isAllowed]` filter
- **Frontend proxy**: `/api/[...path]/route.ts` forwards to `http://localhost:5139`

## Key Conventions
- **UI**: Arabic RTL, Tailwind CSS, FontAwesome icons, font-cairo
- **Z-index**: Header z-[1000], Modals z-[1100]+, Toasts z-[1200]
- **Dates**: `DateHelper.ToHijri()` for Hijri date conversion
- **Email**: `IEmailService.SendEmailAsync(List<string> toEmails, string subject, string body)`
- **FindAllAsync overloads**:
  1. `(criteria)` — simple
  2. `(criteria, skip, take)` — paginated
  3. `(criteria, skip?, take?, orderBy, direction, includes)` — full

## Ports
- Backend API: `http://localhost:5139`
- Frontend: `http://localhost:3001`

## Key Enums
- **ConsultationRequestStatus**: PendingAssignment(0), New(1), InProgress(2), Approved(3), Completed(4), Cancelled(5)
- **CourseStatus**: Draft(1), Published(2), Archived(3)
- **CourseLevel**: Beginner(1), Intermediate(2), Advanced(3)
- **CourseType**: InPerson(0), Online(1), Hybrid(2)
- **LessonType**: Text(0), Video(1), Audio(2), Image(3), Quiz(4), Explanation(5)

## Important Notes
- Must `taskkill //F //IM "Baseqt.API.exe"` before building (DLL lock)
- Use `nohup` for background process stability on Windows bash
- `IEmailService.SendEmailAsync` takes `List<string>` not single string
- Frontend uses `getFileUrl()` from `lib/config` for image URLs
